  "monster": {
    "title": "Plog.",
    "body": "One of the many lords of Pandemonium, Plog has an emaciated body and a ram's head. It changes colour whenever you look at it.\n\n<lightgrey>Max HP: 184     </lightgrey><lightgrey> Will: ++++     </lightgrey><lightgrey>   AC: +        </lightgrey><lightgrey>  EV: ++++ ++++ </lightgrey>                \n<lightgrey>    rF: +..     </lightgrey><lightgrey>   rC: +..      </lightgrey><lightgrey>rPois: +        </lightgrey><lightgrey>rNeg: ∞         </lightgrey><lightgrey>rElec: +        </lightgrey>\n<lightgrey>Threat: Lethal  </lightgrey><lightgrey>Class: Demonic  </lightgrey><lightgrey> Size: Large    </lightgrey><lightgrey> Int: Human     </lightgrey>\nSpeed: 140% (normally travels faster than you)\n\nYou have about 2% to hit with the fire staff of Defence by Offence and 3% to hit with your pseudopods.\nIt has about 72% to hit you.\n\nAttack                 Max Damage         \nHit: distorting touch  42 + 26 (distort)  \n\nIt is immune to torment; and resistant to steam and miasma.\nIt is vulnerable to silver and hated by Zin.\nIt can see invisible.\nIt can open doors.\nSPELLSET_PLACEHOLDERTo read a description, press the key listed above. (AdB) indicates damage (the sum of A B-sided dice), (x%) indicates the chance to defeat your Will, and (y) indicates the spell range; shown in red if you are in range.",
    "quote": "",
    "status": "<white>Not watching you:<lightgrey>\n   This creature has been briefly distracted by something else.\n   \n   <blue>Melee attacks you make against this creature have a chance (proportional to\n   your stealth and weapon skill) of catching it off-guard and dealing increased\n   damage, especially if made with a short blade.<lightgrey>\n\n",
    "spellset": [
      {
